 入則孝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/author-Q1iBAvdMoGVZdNIyHAuy-w">Lý Dục Tú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-S%C4%A9-%C4%90i%E1%BB%83n/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tu%E1%BB%B3-b%C3%ACnh-nam-nhung-v%E1%BB%A5-kinh-H%E1%BB%99i-An-ph%E1%BB%91-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Quan-phu-t%E1%BB%AD-mi%E1%BA%BFu-thi/poem-0vihbiTKp-AvT7G4wTuJRw">Phụng tuỳ bình nam nhung vụ kinh Hội An phố đề Quan phu tử miếu thi - 奉隨平南戎務經會安鋪題關夫子廟詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-S%C4%A9-%C4%90i%E1%BB%83n/author-pfuUA7uGS4qURp0ZBic0fA">Uông Sĩ Điển</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/T%E1%BA%B7ng-T%E1%BA%B1ng-X%C3%A1c-chi-quan-Giao-Ch%E1%BB%89-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-RIK96K7UagJnz6uPF0y4mg">Tặng Tằng Xác chi quan Giao Chỉ kỳ 1 - 客懷贈曾確之官交阯其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/author-HrCILDC9soRz0JVGAcDF9w">Lê Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i/poem-VsuzLp95JE0OMWqtrvsVCA">Xuân nhật cảm hoài - 春日感懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br></div>	</div>
